<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 06:15:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴布亚新几内亚将接待中国、澳大利亚高层访问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/papua-new-guinea-host-china-australia-high-level-visits-2024-04-18/</link><description>预计中国外交部长将在周六访问巴布亚新几内亚时签署一项经济合作协议，就在几天前，澳大利亚总理抵达巴布亚新几内亚，走过一条著名的二战小道，纪念历史性的防务关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 06:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/papua-new-guinea-host-china-australia-high-level-visits-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行警告不要“片面”追求信贷扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cbank-warns-against-one-sided-pursuit-credit-expansion-2024-04-18/</link><description>数据显示银行贷款放缓后，中国央行周四警告称，不要“片面”追求信贷扩张，誓言将优先考虑信贷质量而非规模，并采取措施振兴现有贷款。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 05:44:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cbank-warns-against-one-sided-pursuit-credit-expansion-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>达能超出第一季度销售预期，保持 2024 年目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/danone-q1-sales-beat-forecasts-keeps-2024-goals-2024-04-18/</link><description>达能周四公布的季度销售额强于预期，所有业务均实现销量增长，因为这家全球最大的酸奶制造商设法提高价格以应对更高的投入成本，尽管速度比之前慢。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 05:38:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/danone-q1-sales-beat-forecasts-keeps-2024-goals-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体称，日本在寻求更紧密关系的同时警告中国威胁是“两面派”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-two-faced-seeking-closer-ties-while-warning-china-threat-chinese-state-2024-04-18/</link><description>中国官方报纸周四发表社论，谴责“双面”日本在追求更稳定的双边关系的同时，错误地将其描述为地区安全威胁，并警告称，如果东京鲁莽行事，中国将采取措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 05:26:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-two-faced-seeking-closer-ties-while-warning-china-threat-chinese-state-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>迅达重申2024年销售目标，但警告中国市场疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-posts-q1-order-intake-slightly-above-expectations-2024-04-18/</link><description>电梯和自动扶梯制造商迅达周四重申了全年收入指引，即低个位数百分比增长，尽管该公司在充满挑战的经济背景下下调了对中国新安装电梯的预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 04:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-posts-q1-order-intake-slightly-above-expectations-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟领导人将听取与全球竞争对手抗衡所需的改组</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-leaders-hear-shake-up-needed-match-global-rivals-2024-04-18/</link><description>欧盟领导人将于周四听取欧盟如何采取行动，在新型绿色和数字技术的全球竞赛中赶上美国、中国和其他竞争对手的会议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 04:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-leaders-hear-shake-up-needed-match-global-rivals-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国外长表示北京和雅加达希望地区和平与稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-foreign-minister-says-beijing-jakarta-want-regional-peace-stability-2024-04-18/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周四在雅加达与印度尼西亚外长蕾特诺·马尔苏迪会面后表示，中国和印度尼西亚承诺加强经济联系，维护地区和平与稳定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 03:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-foreign-minister-says-beijing-jakarta-want-regional-peace-stability-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称加强与日本和美国关系的决定是“主权选择”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-says-decision-strengthen-ties-with-japan-us-sovereign-choice-2024-04-18/</link><description>菲律宾外交部周四在回应中国反对三边会议的言论时表示，菲律宾在最近的一次峰会上决定加强与日本和美国的关系，这是该国的“主权选择”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 02:31:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-says-decision-strengthen-ties-with-japan-us-sovereign-choice-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>华为在芯片审查中开始销售新款 Pura 70 智能手机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-huawei-start-selling-pura-70-smartphones-2024-04-18/</link><description>中国科技巨头华为 [RIC:RIC:HWT.UL] 周四开始销售其备受期待的高端 Pura 70 智能手机系列的两款型号，许多分析师预计该系列将采用先进的中国制造芯片，如 Mate 60 手机。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 02:22:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-huawei-start-selling-pura-70-smartphones-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>美元暂停飙升，亚洲股市涨跌互现</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-18/</link><description>周四，亚洲股市涨跌互现，小幅走高，美元稍作喘息，债券市场企稳，投资者开始评估利率前景。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 02:15:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>法国财长表示欧洲必须捍卫工业利益对抗中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/french-finance-minister-says-europe-must-defend-industrial-interests-against-2024-04-17/</link><description>法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔周三表示，欧洲需要“拿出牙齿”来捍卫其工业和贸易利益，对抗中国的生产补贴，但他表示不想发动贸易战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:47:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/french-finance-minister-says-europe-must-defend-industrial-interests-against-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国计划恢复对主导太阳能技术的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-plans-restore-tariffs-dominant-solar-technology-sources-say-2024-04-17/</link><description>两位熟悉白宫的消息人士称，拜登政府预计将批准韩国韩华 Qcells 的请求，撤销为期两年的贸易豁免，该豁免允许从中国和其他国家进口占主导地位的太阳能电池板技术以避免关税计划于周三表示。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:46:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-plans-restore-tariffs-dominant-solar-technology-sources-say-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>F1重返中国面临新挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/f1-faces-fresh-challenge-return-china-2024-04-17/</link><description>一级方程式赛车自 2019 年以来首次重返中国，即使是世界冠军马克斯·维斯塔潘 (Max Verstappen) 在这条 15 年前为他的红牛车队赢得首场大奖赛胜利的赛道上也面临着新的挑战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/f1-faces-fresh-challenge-return-china-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国贸易长官呼吁采取行动保护电动汽车行业免受中国影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ustr-tai-calls-decisive-action-shield-ev-sector-china-2024-04-17/</link><description>美国贸易代表凯瑟琳·戴周三表示，美国必须采取“果断”行动，保护电动汽车免受中国补贴的竞争，她正在完成对特朗普时代中国关税的审查，并考虑乔·拜登总统关于提高进口关税的呼吁中国钢铁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ustr-tai-calls-decisive-action-shield-ev-sector-china-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>拜登呼吁对中国钢铁征收更高关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-call-higher-tariffs-chinese-metals-steel-city-pittsburgh-2024-04-17/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周三呼吁美国大幅提高对中国金属产品的关税，作为旨在取悦摇摆州宾夕法尼亚州钢铁工人的一揽子政策的一部分，但此举可能会激怒北京。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-call-higher-tariffs-chinese-metals-steel-city-pittsburgh-2024-04-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>